     + Added HEADERIMAGES and IMAGESPLACE clauses to GRID and BROWSE.
     + Added ACTIVEX, HOTKEYBOX, PICTURE, PROGRESSMETER, SCROLLBAR,
       TEXTARRAY and XBROWSE.
     ! Fixed: missing clauses from several controls.
